#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:116
msgid ""
"Added ``__builtin_stdc_rotate_left`` and ``__builtin_stdc_rotate_right`` for "
"bit rotation of unsigned integers including ``_BitInt`` types. Rotation "
"counts are normalized modulo the bit-width and support negative values. "
"Usable in constant expressions. Implicit conversion is supported for class/"
"struct types with conversion operators."
msgstr ""

